title: King County Housing Authority Purchases Two Properties near Tukwila Light Rail Station
text: TUKWILA, Wash.--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Due to rising rents, low-income households are being forced to move further away from jobs. KCHA is working to preserve affordable housing within mass transit corridors across King County. ...
